comment: The singleton of the singleton of the empty set is not an ordinal (nor a natural number by ~ omsson ). It can be used to represent an "undefined" value for a partial operation on natural or ordinal numbers. See also ~ onxpdisj . (Contributed by NM, 21-May-2004.)
